headline.main: Deportivo Beats Sporting 1-0, Escapes Relegation Zone
headline.print_headline: Deportivo Beats Sporting 1-0, Escapes Relegation Zone

lead_paragraph: Deportivo La Coruna defeated Sporting Gijon 1-0 in a game between relegation-threatened teams in the Spanish league on Sunday.
